{"tid":118400,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"英超五連敗！雲尼亞里：難以置信！","createTime":"2017-02-13T04:02:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-13T11:28:07.000Z","uid":60281,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ec6773dd980cb282eb60e9e087f01a76297edc6f","tid":118400,"uid":60281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T04:02:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=TytWRGNO3s0Eety5H3eok0kviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=19d7cb09\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】上季英超冠軍李斯特城每況愈下，周日作客史雲斯負0:2，隨時跌落降班區域，領隊雲尼亞里以難以置信來形式球隊下滑狀況。<br />\n<br />\n李斯特城今季早已衛冕無望，近期連續5場聯賽敗北，且6場比賽沒入球，現排第17位，只比尾3的侯城多1分。雲尼亞里（Claudio Ranieri）賽後坦言對球隊持續下滑，感到摸不著頭腦：「我本想在今天展開『新球季』，無奈發展依舊，這是難以置信。他續說：「我們開局不差，也希望取得理想賽果，尤其是面對同樣護級的競爭者，無奈地，史雲斯第一次射門中框，已經打開紀錄，加上半場前再失1球，局面已經非常困難。」李城在歐聯躋身16強，又殺入英足盃16強，被問到是否早已準備「棄聯賽、攻盃賽」，雲帥說：「我的注意力仍在英超，英足盃和歐聯是截然不同的舞台，己隊希望在聯賽表現回穩，安全地留在英超。」"},{"pid":"dbafc73c6aa1ea31fddb07486153ab9c65ec7539","tid":118400,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T04:03:35.000Z","msg":"唔使驚 黎緊利物浦會幫你反底"},{"pid":"08df685e5807ffa699f2d522cad917ca0ab04b54","tid":118400,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T04:04:16.000Z","msg":"潮文 潛力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"339e708e29bc16463e4f3277eb2706f1fb3cb8fa","tid":118400,"uid":32707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T04:06:16.000Z","msg":"英冠見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de5e39632e34214039b6319318a854ad0976e713","tid":118400,"uid":23878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T04:08:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" cla